<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5549151>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Negoescuanthura bastidai n. sp., holotype, female, 14.3 mm, UMAR-PERA 566, Estacahuite Beach, Oaxaca. A) Body, dorsal view; B) telson; C) antennula; D) antenna with detail of sucker-like cuticular structures; E) mandible with detail of" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5549151/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5549157>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Colanthura gabinae n. sp., holotype, female, 2.7 mm, UMAR-PERA 572, La Roqueta Island, Guerrero. A) Body, dorsal view; B) pleon; C) telson; D) antennula; E) antenna; F) mandible; G) maxilla; H) maxilliped." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5549157/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5549165>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Paranthura amorensis n. sp., holotype, female, 5.7 mm, UMAR-PERA 581, Playa del Amor, Zipolite, Oaxaca.A) Body, dorsal view with detail of the telson; B) antennula; C) antenna; D) mandible; E) maxilla; F) maxilliped; G) pereopod 1; H) palm of pereopod 1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5549165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5549173>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. P. tientai n. sp., Holotype, female, 7.4 mm, UMAR-PERA 579, El Arrocito Beach, Oaxaca.A) Body, dorsal view and detail of telson; B) antennula; C) antenna with detail of flagellum; D) mandible; E) maxilla; F) maxilliped." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5549173/files/figure.png" ;
